[Well, it appears as though there is continued circulation of the WPV1 in Pakistan and Afghanistan as seen by the reports of positive environmental samples in multiple locations. As for the cVDPV outbreaks, it appears as though there is continued circulation of the cVDPVs in Nigeria and in Papua New Guinea. The dates of onset of cases in Papua New Guinea thus far are those where exposure to the viruses could have occurred prior to the implementation of control measures.

